show.description: Left heartbroken on her wedding day, a woman crosses paths with the man who once rejected her—now a CEO battling insomnia. Unaware of their shared past, fate draws them together again through an unexpected professional connection. A heartwarming and humorous journey of healing, rediscovery, and love that deserves a second chance.
